          <title>Doncic and James score 30+ each for 1st time this season in Lakers' 128-121 win over Grizzlies</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Luka Doncic and LeBron James topped 30 points each in the same game for the first time this season as the Los Angeles Lakers rallied for a 128-121 victory over the Memphis Grizzlies.]]></description>
